    <string name="about_app">About App</string>
    <string name="about_app_description">Smart Home is a comprehensive IoT solution designed to give you full control over your home environment. Connect seamlessly to ESP32 devices, manage your lighting, and customize your experience with multi-language support and personalized themes. Your home, smarter and more secure than ever.</string>
    <string name="about_us">About Us</string>
    <string name="about_us_description">We are two students from the University of Badji Mokhtar Annaba. This Smart Home application is our third-year graduation project. Our vision is to move forward with this project and give everyone the chance to experience a life with a step into the future through accessible and innovative home automation.</string>
